definitions: Be successful or victorious in (a contest or conflict)
Acquire or secure as a result of a contest, conflict, bet, or other endeavour.
Gain (a person's attention, support, or love), typically gradually or by effort.
Gain the support or favour of someone by action or persuasion.
Manage to succeed or achieve something by effort.
Manage to reach (a place) by effort.
Dry (hay) by exposure to the air.
